{"tid":1881903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國外長勒德里昂表示，不會採取和容忍任何對中國人歧視性行為，將繼續予以冷靜理性應對。","createTime":"2020-02-15T22:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T22:36:03.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5ab5219cf9b0ad5dd02d14e69707331d5011c7","tid":1881903,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508810-20200216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508810-20200216.htm&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFxz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=49295eb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508810-20200216.htm&h=b204169e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508810-20200216.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外長王毅向法國外長勒德里昂表示，抗擊疫情的各項舉措已經取得明顯成效，疫情過後中國經濟將會更加健康可持續發展。<br />\n<br />\n雙方在德國慕尼黑安全會議期間會晤。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》報道，勒德里昂表示，法方不會採取和容忍任何歧視性措施，將繼續予以冷靜理性應對。<br />\n<br />\n另外，王毅亦與歐洲議會人民黨黨團主席韋伯會晤。<br />\n<br />\n王毅重申，中國正在深化改革，擴大開放，將為歐洲企業提供更多機遇。"},{"pid":"d241115a0de374e6c55b59d1984c25cf163d421d","tid":1881903,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:23:52.000Z","msg":"改革左廿年重講心深化改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef0ad5ba7aaf133e54c975d2b80082925f7d2d1","tid":1881903,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:26:51.000Z","msg":"法國佬： I love 人民幣"},{"pid":"248fbb6a075d23d8077bb7b7bf6bda18a52a0551","tid":1881903,"uid":231725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:36:03.000Z","msg":"咁奶共陣間法國都感染左法國佬政變都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}